OL,3,CFootball pitch to be built in honour
OL,4,Cof teenage player stabbed to death
OL,6,FAn artificial pitch is to be built in
OL,7,Fhonour of a football-loving teenager
OL,8,Fwho was stabbed to death.
OL,10,FThe 3G pitch will be built in
OL,11,FGateshead in the memory of Tomasz
OL,12,FOleszak following a #868,000 grant
OL,13,Ffrom the Football Foundation ` a
OL,14,Fcharity backed by the Premier League,
OL,15,Fthe FA and the Government.
OL,17,FTomasz was just 14 when he was stabbed
OL,18,Fto death in 2022 by a 15-year-old who
OL,19,Fshouted in triumph after he carried
OL,20,Fout the fatal attack. The killer was
OL,21,Fjailed for life in 2023.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
