OL,3,CFootball pitch to be built in honour
OL,4,Cof teenage player stabbed to death
OL,6,FFor much of his childhood, Tomasz
OL,7,Fplayed football for Gateshead
OL,8,FCleveland Hall Community Association.
OL,10,FThe club will now build a floodlit
OL,11,Fartificial pitch at its premises at
OL,12,FBeacon Lough and this will allow the
OL,13,Forganisation to expand into disability
OL,14,Fand walking football.
OL,16,FThe pitch will also be exclusively
OL,17,Fused by women's and girls' teams on
OL,18,Fone day of the week.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
