CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1780488669
OL,3,CFootball pitch to be built in honour
OL,4,Cof teenage player stabbed to death
OL,6,FAndrew Watling, leader of Gateshead
OL,7,FCleveland Hall CA, said: "The loss of
OL,8,FTomasz hit everyone at our club
OL,9,Fextremely hard.
OL,11,F"I am delighted that the Football
OL,12,FFoundation have chosen to support our
OL,13,Fproject to build a lasting monument to
OL,14,Fhis memory and a permanent reminder of
OL,15,Fthe horrendous consequences of knife
OL,16,Fcrime.
OL,18,F"The pitch will provide the
OL,19,Fopportunity for thousands of
OL,20,Fyoungsters to participate in sport
OL,21,Fover the decades to come."
OL,26,@oD@ZOUsD@AOUzD@AOU}D@ZO]
