OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1780488669
OL,3,CFootball pitch to be built in honour
OL,4,Cof teenage player stabbed to death
OL,6,FKim McGuinness, North East Mayor,
OL,7,Fsaid: "This pitch will stand as a
OL,8,Ftribute to Tomasz ` a young boy who
OL,9,Floved his football and his club.
OL,11,F"His loss is still felt deeply in the
OL,12,Flocal community, but it's right that
OL,13,Fhis memory will live on here, in a
OL,14,Fplace that brings people together and
OL,15,Fhelps the next generation grow, on and
OL,16,Foff the pitch."
OL,26,@oD@GOUsD@AOUxD@OO]
